     <p><a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/2012/NOTE-WCAG20-TECHS-20120103/H57" rel="external" title="WCAG 2.0, Technique H57"><big>Default language</big></a> using the <code>lang</code> attribute in the <code>&lt;html&gt;</code> element</p>
    </li>
