     <p><a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/2012/NOTE-UNDERSTANDING-WCAG20-20120103/meaning-other-lang-id.html" rel="external" title="3.1.2 Language of Parts"><big>Change of language</big></a> using the <code>lang</code> atrribute in <strong>any</strong> element enclosing the text in a different language.</p>
    </li>
   </ul>
   <p>When using the <code>lang</code> attribute, use:</p>
   <ul>
    <li><code>en</code> for English</li>
    <li><code>fr</code> for French</li>
    <li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_ISO_639-1_codes">These codes</a> for other languages <small>(see 639-1 column)</small></li>
